# crlf-basic

## Input

```
key value
foo bar

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..20
  ENTRY@0..11
    WORD_KEY@0..3
      WORD@0..3 "key"
    SPACE@3..4 " "
    LINE_STRING@4..9
      STRING@4..9 "value"
    NEWLINE@9..11 "\r\n"
  ENTRY@11..20
    WORD_KEY@11..14
      WORD@11..14 "foo"
    SPACE@14..15 " "
    LINE_STRING@15..18
      STRING@15..18 "bar"
    NEWLINE@18..20 "\r\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..3 "key",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@4..9 "value",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@11..14 "foo",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@15..18 "bar",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

